NAME

DateTime::Locale::fy_NL - Locale data examples for the Western Frisian Netherlands (fy-NL) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Western Frisian Netherlands locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = tiisdei 5 Febrewaris 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = freed 22 Desimber 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = sneon 15 Septimber -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Febrewaris 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Desimber 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Septimber -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Feb 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Des 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Sep -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05-02-08
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22-12-95
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15-09--10
